Name: Lunchroom Leut
Review Text: Decent freshly-made sandwiches, although a little overpriced. Service can be friendly or unfriendly depending on their mood. It's basically the only option around here, other than a long walk to the supermarkets.

Name: Lunchroom Leut
Review Text: Very handy small lunch restaurant in the middle of Corporate Amsterdam-West. Excellent value for money. Masters of alliteration in the naming of the sandwiches. Good outdoor seating as well. Worth a stroll from The Office.
